OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The transport secretary says he hopes  
OL,6, to change the Covid tests people coming
OL,7, into the UK must take before families  
OL,8, return from half-term holidays.        
OL,10,FBut Grant Shapps did not give a date   
OL,11,Ffor when expensive PCR tests would be  
OL,12,Fswapped for cheaper lateral flow tests.
OL,14,FCurrently, fully vaccinated adults     
OL,15,Fentering the UK must take a PCR test   
OL,16,Fwithin two days of arriving.           
OL,18,FHe also defended cutting the travel red
OL,19,Flist to seven countries, saying        
OL,20,Fvaccines "massively reduced" the risks.
